@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vfsmoa(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.80
    v0 = wp.cos(tmp)
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.sin((v0 + 0.75 + v2 + 0.70)))
    v2 = wp.exp(tmp)
    tmp = (0.09 / 0.80)
    v2 = (wp.abs(0.68) + (wp.sin(v2 + 0.98) + (v1 + 0.48 * v2 + 0.49)))
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.07 + tmp + 0.35) + 0.94) / v1)
    data[tid] = v0
